Title: Deep Throat
Plot: Mulder and Scully head to Ellens Air Force Base to investigate the mysterious case of a military test pilot who disappeared after experiencing strange psychotic behavior. While on the case, Mulder meets a mysterious man dubbed "Deep Throat" who claims to have classified information about his investigations into the paranormal.
GuestStars: Michael Bryan French, Seth Green, Gabrielle Rose, Andrew Johnston, Lalainia Lindejerg, Vince Metcalfe, Doc Harris, Jon Cuthbert, Brian Furlong, Michael Puttonen, Sheila Moore, Monica Parker
